snippet.title: Random Madness
snippet.description:
Hey, I`m Valentin The Mad, a musician (rock-prog-metal solo artist), and this is my gaming channel, Random Madness.

The channel is mainly centered around response mechanics in video games - be it character responses (which is gore in most cases), or responses on the environment - destruction effects and physics.

There are demonstrations, discussion videos (currently done in an impressions format), mod videos and interviews with developers about their upcoming projects.

PC specs:
i7 6700 
Gigabyte RTX 2070 Windforce
16 gigs of DDR4 RAM
Edirol UA-25 sound card

Microphones:
Rode NT1
Shure SM58
